  "title": "Executive Secretary for Nanyang Hwu Clan General Association",
  "description": "<p>1. Draft and prepare general correspondence letters and general notices to the members  (in English and Chinese) for the Association </p><p>2. Plan and run the various events and activities organised by the Association </p><p>3. Plan, schedule and attend routine Board meetings and other work related meetings. Record and prepare the meeting minutes. (in English and Chinese)</p><p>4. Administer the monthly regular income and expenditures records.</p><p>5. Proficient in MS Word, Excel, PowerPoint & social media platforms.</p><p>Applicant shall be Singaporean or PR & is able work independently. </p>",
